        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>When steered, the outer section of each Fabco Steerable Drive End rotates about the kingpin
                    centerline. The U-joint, centered on the kingpin centerline, allows power to be transmitted while
                    turning.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
